TAKE A 3D TOUR
Debauchery is Downtown Melbourne's premiere live music venue with full liquor bar, and the largest craft beer selection, featuring 37 draughts and over 130 select flavors.
Open 7 days a week from 1pm til 2am. We are available for private parties, special events and catering; dog friendly, and outside food is welcome! Come visit the hottest spot in downtown Melbourne!
